The,Events,API,allows,developers,to,build,applications,that,respond,to,activities,in,Slack,User,and,bot,based,event,subscriptions,can,be,received,in,JSON,format,Once,event,types,are,specified,Slack,will,provide,a,stream,of,data,with,this,RESTful,API,This,API,uses,OAuth,for,authentication,developers,need,to,register,their,applications,to,obtain,a,Client,ID,and,Client,Secret,for,response,procedures